<%= render "/layouts/page_title", page_title: "Applications", page_subtitle: "" %>
<section id="content">
  <div class="content-wrap">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-2"></div>
      <div class="col-md-8">
      <%= link_to "Back to Index", applications_path %>
        <table class="table table-striped">
          <tr>
            <th>First Name:</th>
            <th><%= @application.first_name %></th> 
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th>Last Name:</th>
            <th><%= @application.last_name %></th> 
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th>Email:</th>
            <th><%= @application.email %></th> 
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th>Phone:</th>
            <th><%= @application.phone %></th> 
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th>Location(s):</th>
            <th><%= @application.locations.pluck(:name).join(", ") %></th> 
          </tr>        
          <tr>
            <th>Application Sent:</th>
            <th><%= @application.applications_human_time %></th> 
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th>How did you hear about Anyone Can Learn To Code?:</th>
            <th><%= @application.learn_about_acltc %></th> 
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th>Tell us more about what you're currently doing (job or school, etc.):</th>
            <th><%= @application.current_occupation %></th> 
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th>What are your primary goals in learning how to code?:</th>
            <th><%= @application.primary_goals %></th> 
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th>Do you have any previous programming experience? Working on online tutorials certainly counts!:</th>
            <th><%= @application.programming_experience %></th> 
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th>If you were seeking a job in web development, in what city do you want to work?:</th>
            <th><%= @application.preferred_work_location %></th> 
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th>Is there a specific project you would like to work on for your capstone project?:</th>
            <th><%= @application.capstone_idea %></th> 
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th>Will you keep your job during the bootcamp? If so, how do you realistically plan to do both?:</th>
            <th><%= @application.work_concurrently %></th> 
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th>Programming requires complex problem solving and logical analysis, and the ability to tinker around with something until it works. Give examples of when youâ€™ve had these experiences.:</th>
            <th><%= @application.tinker_example %></th> 
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th>Why should we accept you over well-qualified candidates?:</th>
            <th><%= @application.why_better %></th> 
          </tr>
        </table>

      </div>
      <div class="col-md-2"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>